Rtractor — third-party code attribution
========================================

This file records the provenance of reference implementations wrapped or
ported into Rtractor, per the terms of their original licenses.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
src/embed.cpp (fnn_fraction_cpp, used by estimate_embed_dim)  (clean-room
reimplementation from the published algorithm -- not a translation of
any licensed or specified source)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Algorithm: Kennel MB, Brown R, Abarbanel HDI. Determining embedding
dimension for phase-space reconstruction using a geometrical
construction. Phys Rev A 1992;45:3403-3411.

No reference implementation was specified for this port (asked; no
preference given), so this was implemented directly from the published
algorithm description rather than validated against another codebase.
Sanity-checked structurally only (monotonic decrease of the FNN fraction
with embedding dimension for a known low-dimensional system), not
validated against an independent implementation -- treat with more
caution than the other entries in this file until cross-checked.

