R/embed.R (embed_time_series, estimate_delay)  (clean-room
reimplementations from the published algorithms)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Algorithms:
  Takens F. Detecting strange attractors in turbulence. In: Dynamical
  Systems and Turbulence, Warwick 1980. Lecture Notes in Mathematics,
  vol 898. Springer; 1981:366-381.

  Fraser AM, Swinney HL. Independent coordinates for strange attractors
  from mutual information. Phys Rev A 1986;33:1134-1140.

No reference implementation was specified for either function; both are
straightforward, unambiguous translations of their respective published
formulas (delay embedding is a direct index construction; mutual
information is a standard binned-histogram estimator), so parity
validation against a second implementation was judged unnecessary here,
unlike the FNN entry above.

